      *                          * Test se pagina da trattare          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   snp-pie-reg-000      thru snp-pie-reg-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se no : decremento ulteriore, a me- *
      *                          *         no di non essere a pagina 1 *
      *                          *         caso in cui si va' ad ac-   *
      *                          *         cettazione corpo            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-snx    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-610.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo ad impostazione piede       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-nok-reg-600.
       acc-nok-reg-650.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se spostamento a pagina successiva      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Salvataggio numero pagina attuale   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-sts-imp-npp    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-spp      .
       acc-nok-reg-660.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Status di impostazione dati della   *
      *                          * della pagina attuale a : si'        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-ppx
                                              (w-cnt-sts-imp-npp)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se la pagina attuale e' la massima  *
      *                          * si pone lo status di impostazione   *
      *                          * dati generale piede a si'           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npp    not  < w-cnt-sts-imp-mpp
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-pie      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se la pagina attuale e' la massima  *
      *                          * si va' a conferma impostazioni      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npp    not  < w-cnt-sts-imp-mpp
                     move  w-cnt-sts-imp-spp
                                          to   w-cnt-sts-imp-npp
                     go to acc-nok-reg-800.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Incremento numero pagina attuale    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-sts-imp-npp      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test se pagina da trattare          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   snp-pie-reg-000      thru snp-pie-reg-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se no : a re-incremento             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-snx    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-660.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Status di visualizzazione prompts e *
      *                          * dati della pagina impostata a : no  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-ppx
                                              (w-cnt-sts-imp-spp)     .
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-vis-ppx
                                              (w-cnt-sts-imp-spp)     .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo ad impostazione piede       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-nok-reg-600.
       acc-nok-reg-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conferma impostazioni                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in Off                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se attualmente visualizzato il corpo si e-  *
      *                  * segue la visualizzazione dei prompts della  *
      *                  * riga corpo espansa                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor    =    spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-805.
           perform   pmt-rig-cor-000      thru pmt-rig-cor-999        .
       acc-nok-reg-805.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Cancellazione eventuali note operative      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NT"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in On                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       acc-nok-reg-810.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se sola visualizzazione                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "V"
                     go to acc-nok-reg-820
           else      go to acc-nok-reg-830.
       acc-nok-reg-820.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione se sola visualizzazione    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "MX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      "#VIS"               to   v-not                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           move      "E"                  to   v-msk                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "EXIT"               to   v-pfk (20)             .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           if        v-key                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-840.
           if        v-alf                =    "E"
                     move  "EXIT"         to   v-key                  .
           go to     acc-nok-reg-840.
       acc-nok-reg-830.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione se inserimento o modifica  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "MX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
      *
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-tes    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-cor    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-pie    not  = spaces
                     move  "#SAP"         to   v-not
                     move  "SNEP"         to   v-msk
                     move  "DO  "         to   v-pfk (05)
           else      move  "#SAV"         to   v-not
                     move  "SNE"          to   v-msk                  .
      *
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Tasto Print                         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Normalizzazione flag            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-mst-flg          .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Test                            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-imp    =    "K"
                     go to acc-nok-reg-835.
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "M" or
                     w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "V"
                     move  "PRNT"         to   v-pfk (18)
                     go to acc-nok-reg-835.
           if        v-pfk (05)           =    "DO  "
                     move  "PRNT"         to   v-pfk (18)             .
       acc-nok-reg-835.
           move      "EXIT"               to   v-pfk (20)             .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           if        v-key                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-840.
           if        v-alf                =    "S"
                     move   "DO  "        to   v-key
           else if   v-alf                =    "E"
                     move   "E"           to   w-cnt-tus-acc-nok
                     go to acc-nok-reg-999
           else if   v-alf                =    "N"
                     move   "UP  "        to   v-key
           else if   v-alf                =    "P"
                     move   "PRNT"        to   v-key                  .
       acc-nok-reg-840.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su risposta dell'utente                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     go to acc-nok-reg-850
           else if   v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to acc-nok-reg-860
           else if   v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-nok-reg-870
           else if   v-key                =    "PRNT"
                     go to acc-nok-reg-880
           else      go to acc-nok-reg-810.
       acc-nok-reg-850.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Do                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-nok      .
           perform   cnt-tdo-nok-000      thru cnt-tdo-nok-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-870.
           go to     acc-nok-reg-999.
       acc-nok-reg-860.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Exit                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Subroutine di controllo per Exit        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se Exit non attivato : come 'Up'    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-exi-000  thru exe-acc-cmp-exi-999    .
           if        w-cnt-acc-flg-exi    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-nok-reg-870.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se Exit attivato                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "E"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-nok      .
           go to     acc-nok-reg-999.
       acc-nok-reg-870.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Up                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazione piede                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
           go to     acc-nok-reg-640.
       acc-nok-reg-880.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Print                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-mst-flg          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se in funzione di 'Visualizzazione' :   *
      *                      * uscita come per 'Exit', altrimenti u-   *
      *                      * scita come per 'Do'                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "V"
                     go to acc-nok-reg-860
           else      go to acc-nok-reg-850.
       acc-nok-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Trattamento testata registrazione                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "pgm/bol/prg/cpy/pbol3000.tes"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Trattamento corpo registrazione                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "pgm/bol/prg/cpy/pbol3000.cor"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Trattamento piede registrazione                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "pgm/bol/prg/cpy/pbol3000.pie"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo su impostazione tasto Do campi chiave           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-key-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tdo-key-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo movimento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb        not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-100.
           move      "Manca il tipo movimento !                         
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-key-900.
       cnt-tdo-key-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su data documento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dat-doc        not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-150.
           move      "Manca la data documento !                         
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-key-900.
       cnt-tdo-key-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se numero documento a zero                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-num-doc        not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se causale di magazzino non esistente : ol- *
      *                  * tre                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb-cam    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test sulla data di registrazione, che   *
      *                      * non sia inferiore alla data di regi-    *
      *                      * strazione minima di MAG                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dat-doc        not  < w-gen-dtr-min
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-200.
           move      "Data di registrazione non accettabile !           
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-key-900.
       cnt-tdo-key-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su sottoconto iva vendite                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpf-siv    not  = zero or
                     w-ref-stc-ivv-cod    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-300.
           move      "Sottoconto iva vendite indeterminato !            
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-key-900.
       cnt-tdo-key-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Completamento numero documento              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Secolo/Anno                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-doc        to   s-dat                  .
           move      s-saa                to   w-tes-num-doc-saa      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero giornale iva o codice dipendenza:*
      *                      * se il documento e' anche fattura e' il  *
      *                      * numero giornale iva; altrimenti e' il   *
      *                      * codice dipendenza                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb-mif    =    03
                     move  w-tes-tip-mpf-ngi
                                          to   w-tes-num-doc-god
           else      move  w-tes-cod-dpz  to   w-tes-num-doc-god      .
       cnt-tdo-key-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dichiarazione di inizio ciclo evasione ordini   *
      *              * clienti                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se gestione ordini clienti attiva      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-orc-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se tipo movimento per la bolla lo pre- *
      *                  * vede                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb-maf    not  = 02
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Esecuzione                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DI"                 to   l-eva-orc-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/bol/prg/obj/pbol300a"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-eva-orc
                                               w-prs
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
       cnt-tdo-key-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dichiarazione di inizio ciclo evasione ordini   *
      *              * di spedizione                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se gestione ordini di spedizione atti- *
      *                  * va                                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-ods-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se tipo movimento per la bolla lo pre- *
      *                  * vede                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb-maf    not  = 03
                     go to cnt-tdo-key-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Esecuzione                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DI"                 to   l-eva-ods-tip-ope      .
           move      "pgm/bol/prg/obj/pbol300b"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using l-eva-ods
                                               w-prs
                                               w-tes
                                               w-pie
                                               w-rig
                                               w-cat-rig              .
       cnt-tdo-key-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione eventuale default per bolla da du- *
      *              * plicare                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpf-tdo    not  = 03
                     move  w-tes-tip-mpb  to   l-dup-rdb-cod-tmb      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prompt per tipo fornitura                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-frn-000      thru pmt-tip-frn-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prompt per data documento se reso da cliente    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dri-mgd-000      thru pmt-dri-mgd-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prompt per numero documento se reso da cliente  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-nri-mgd-000      thru pmt-nri-mgd-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita per controlli superati                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-key-999.
       cnt-tdo-key-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento errore                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di uscita ad errore                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-key-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-key-999.
           exit.
           
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo se chiave vuota                                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-key-vuo-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-key-vuo-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpb        =    spaces and
                     w-tes-dat-doc        =    zero   and
                     w-tes-num-doc        =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-key-vuo-flg      .
       cnt-key-vuo-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo su impostazione tasto Do campi non chiave       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-nok-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-nok-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Indirizzo di spedizione             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-arc (1)    =    "A" or
                     w-tes-tip-arc (1)    =    "N" or
                     w-tes-tip-arc (1)    =    spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-020.
           if        w-tes-tip-mpf-tdo    =    03
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-020.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ids (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-020.
           move      "Indirizzo di spedizione indeterminato !           
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-020.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Indirizzo di spedizione manuale     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-ids (1)    not  = 02
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-030.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-rag-ids (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-030.
           move      "Indirizzo di spedizione manuale incompleto !      
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-030.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : cliente per fatturazione            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-040.
           if        w-tes-arc-plf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-040.
           move      "Manca la definizione del cliente per fatturazione 
      -              "!              "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-040.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Sigla valuta per fatturazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-050.
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-050.
           move      "Manca la definizione della sigla valuta per fattur
      -              "azione !       "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Tipo vendita per l'agente           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da trattare                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-070.
           if        w-prs-age-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-070.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fsp-doc (1)    =    02
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-070.
           if        w-tes-cod-age (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-070.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-vpa (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-070.
           move      "Manca la definizione del tipo vendita per l'agente
      -              " !             "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-070.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Flag di significativita' dati prov- *
      *              * vigionali per il documento                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da trattare                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-080.
           if        w-prs-age-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-080.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-age (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-080.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fsp-doc (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-080.
           move      "Si/No provvigioni per il documento indeterminato !
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-080.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo : Provvigione a forfait per il docu-  *
      *              * mento                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da trattare                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-090.
           if        w-prs-age-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-090.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fsp-doc (1)    not  = 03
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-085.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-pvf-age (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-090.
           move      "Manca l'importo provvigione a forfait per il docum
      -              "ento !         "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-085.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se controllo da effettuare             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fsp-doc (1)    not  = 04
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-090.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-pvf-age (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-090.
           move      "Manca la % di provvigione a forfait per il documen
      -              "to !           "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-090.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se gestione consegne                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ipc-sub-pgm-ind    =    "CM"
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo righe del documento                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-rig-doc-000      thru ctl-rig-doc-999        .
           if        w-ctl-rig-doc-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-950.
       cnt-tdo-nok-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda se il tipo movimento inte- *
      *              * ressa la fatturazione o no                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-200
           else if   w-tes-int-ftr        =    02
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-400
           else if   w-tes-int-ftr        =    03
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-600.
       cnt-tdo-nok-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo movimento : non interessa la fatturazione  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nessun controllo                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-999.
       cnt-tdo-nok-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo movimento : da fatturare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totale righe                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tot-rig-000      thru det-tot-rig-999        .
           if        w-det-tot-rig-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-950.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione % di sconto in chiusura      *
      *                  * in base ad eventuali scaglioni di ammontare *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-scg-scc-000      thru det-scg-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione codici iva per piede         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-civ-pie-000      thru det-civ-pie-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totali riepilogo documento   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tri-doc-000      thru det-tri-doc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Compattamento castelletto iva               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-cst-iva-000      thru cmp-cst-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Compattamento castelletto contropartite     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-cst-ctp-000      thru cmp-cst-ctp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione inoltro documenti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-inl-dcm (1)    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-tes-inl-dcm (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione inoltro pagamenti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-inl-pgt (1)    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-tes-inl-pgt (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo dello sconto incondizionato       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-tot-scc-000      thru ctl-tot-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo relativo all'eventuale plafond    *
      *                  * dichiarato con lettera d'intenti            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-plf-lic-000      thru ctl-plf-lic-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-999.
       cnt-tdo-nok-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo movimento : e' anche una fattura           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totale righe                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tot-rig-000      thru det-tot-rig-999        .
           if        w-det-tot-rig-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-950.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione % di sconto in chiusura      *
      *                  * in base ad eventuali scaglioni di ammontare *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-scg-scc-000      thru det-scg-scc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione codici iva per piede         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-civ-pie-000      thru det-civ-pie-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione totali riepilogo documento   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tri-doc-000      thru det-tri-doc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Compattamento castelletto iva               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-cst-iva-000      thru cmp-cst-iva-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Compattamento castelletto contropartite     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-cst-ctp-000      thru cmp-cst-ctp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su numero elementi in castelletto iva  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-iva-ele (1)    not  > 6
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-620.
           move      "Numero elementi in castelletto iva oltre il massim
      -              "o !            "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-620.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su numero elementi in castelletto con- *
      *                  * tropartite                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-ctp-ele (1)    not  > 10
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-640.
           move      "Esubero elementi in castelletto contropartite !   
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-640.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se documento a zero                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-tot-doc (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-660.
           move      "Documento a zero !                                
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-660.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se documento negativo                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-tot-doc (1)    >    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-680.
           if        w-tes-cod-fop (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-680.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Controllo che i codici pagamento asso-  *
      *                      * ciati alla forma di pagamento siano a   *
      *                      * zero                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-pag (1, 1) =    zero and
                     w-tes-cod-pag (1, 2) =    zero and
                     w-tes-cod-pag (1, 3) =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-680.
           move      "Forma di pagamento non ammessa per documenti negat
      -              "ivi            "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-680.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se nota di accredito                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mpf-tdo    not  = 03
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-700.
           if        w-tes-cod-fop (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-700.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Controllo che i codici pagamento asso-  *
      *                      * ciati alla forma di pagamento se non    *
      *                      * sono a zero, siano di tipo Rimessa Di-  *
      *                      * retta                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-pag (1, 1) not  = zero and
                     w-tes-tip-pag (1, 1) not  =  01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-700.
           if        w-tes-cod-pag (1, 2) not  = zero and
                     w-tes-tip-pag (1, 2) not  =  01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-700.
           if        w-tes-cod-pag (1, 3) not  = zero and
                     w-tes-tip-pag (1, 3) not  =  01
                     go to cnt-tdo-nok-700.
           move      "Forma di pagamento non ammessa per Note di Accredi
      -              "to             "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-900.
       cnt-tdo-nok-700.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione inoltro documenti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-inl-dcm (1)    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-tes-inl-dcm (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione inoltro pagamenti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-inl-pgt (1)    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-tes-inl-pgt (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione scadenze del documento       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-sca-doc-000      thru det-sca-doc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuali assestamenti scadenze manuali     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   exe-exp-pie-ass-000  thru exe-exp-pie-ass-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controllo relativo all'eventuale plafond    *
      *                  * dichiarato con lettera d'intenti            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-plf-lic-000      thru ctl-plf-lic-999        .
       cnt-tdo-nok-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-nok-999.
       cnt-tdo-nok-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento errore                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
       cnt-tdo-nok-950.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di uscita ad errore                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-nok-999.
           exit.
           
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutine di eventuale controllo su plafond cliente se   *
      *    * dichiarato in lettera d'intenti                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       ctl-plf-lic-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se controllo da effettuare                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su personalizzazione                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-snx-lic        not  = "S"
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test sulle date di riferimento della lette- *
      *                  * ra d'intenti                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-lic-dri    =    zero or
                     w-let-arc-lic-drf    =    zero
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se il documento ricade entro gli       *
      *                  * estremi della lettera d'intenti             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dat-doc        < w-let-arc-lic-dri or
                     w-tes-dat-doc        > w-let-arc-lic-drf
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su plafond                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-lic-plf    =    zero
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-900.
       ctl-plf-lic-080.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni preliminari                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-imp-vlb-plf      .   
           move      zero                 to   w-det-imp-vlb-tib      .   
       ctl-plf-lic-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scansione bolle emesse nel range di date        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-plf-lic-bol-000  thru ctl-plf-lic-bol-999    .
       ctl-plf-lic-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo vero e proprio                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su tipo assoggettamento IVA del docu-  *
      *                  * mento in corso di trattamento               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-ass-iva (1)    =    zero
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-520.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Cumulo del documento in trattamento         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       w-pie-tot-ibl (1)    to   w-det-imp-vlb-plf      .
       ctl-plf-lic-520.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Confronto tra plafond e sommatoria imponi-  *
      *                  * bili gia' fatturati nel periodo con il do-  *
      *                  * cumento in corso di trattamento             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-imp-vlb-plf    not  > w-let-arc-lic-plf
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-900.
       ctl-plf-lic-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio immagine video                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in Off                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Box                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      04                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      77                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione messaggio nel box              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing fatturato cliente               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      10                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<BG"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-det-imp-vlb-plf    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      65                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "Esubero del Plafond ("
                                          to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ") ! ('S' per conferma)"
                                          to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-csb-000      thru all-str-csb-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Messaggio nel box                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      65                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in On                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       ctl-plf-lic-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione function key                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Accettazione per presa visione              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      74                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su carattere accettato             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        v-alf                not  = "S" and
                     v-alf                not  = "s"
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ripristino immagine video                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       ctl-plf-lic-820.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di uscita ad errore                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg      .
       ctl-plf-lic-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-plf-lic-999.
       ctl-plf-lic-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutine di eventuale controllo su plafond cliente se   *
      *    * dichiarato in lettera d'intenti                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Ciclo di scansione bolle da fatturare                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-000.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su file [bit]                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "DPZARCDAT "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-tes-cod-dpz        to   rf-bit-cod-dpz         .
           move      "C"                  to   rf-bit-tip-arc         .
           move      w-tes-arc-plf (1)    to   rf-bit-cod-arc         .
           move      w-let-arc-lic-dri    to   rf-bit-dat-doc         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-bit-num-doc         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-bit-num-prt         .
           move      "pgm/bol/fls/ioc/obj/iofbit"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-bit                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Start errata : a controllo               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-900.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale file [bit]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/bol/fls/ioc/obj/iofbit"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-bit                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine file : a controllo                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-900.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-cod-dpz       not  = w-tes-cod-dpz     or
                     rf-bit-tip-arc       not  = "C"               or
                     rf-bit-cod-arc       not  = w-tes-arc-plf (1) or
                     rf-bit-dat-doc       >    w-let-arc-lic-drf
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-900.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezioni sul record                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su numero documento, che non sia quel- *
      *                  * lo in corso di trattamento                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-num-doc       =    w-tes-num-doc
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test documento da sottoporre a fatturazione *
      *                  * differita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-int-ftr       not  = 02
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su tipo assoggettamento IVA            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-ass-iva       =    zero
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se documento gia' fatturato            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
______*    if        rf-bit-fat-dat       not  = zero or
______*              rf-bit-fat-num       not  = zero or
______*              rf-bit-fat-npb       not  = zero
______*              go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-420.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accumulo plafond per scansione del castelletto  *
      *              * Iva                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-imp-vlb-ctr      .
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-422.
           add       1                    to   w-det-imp-vlb-ctr      .
           if        w-det-imp-vlb-ctr    >    6
                     go to ctl-plf-lic-bol-800.
           add       rf-bit-iva-ibl
                    (w-det-imp-vlb-ctr)   to   w-det-imp-vlb-plf      .
           go to     ctl-plf-lic-bol-422.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-plf-lic-bol-200.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-plf-lic-bol-999.
       ctl-plf-lic-bol-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo righe del documento                             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       ctl-rig-doc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-ctl-rig-doc-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio area w-rig                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig                to   w-sav-wrk-rig          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio area catena                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig            to   w-sav-cat-rig          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione risposta da operatore           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to    w-ctl-rig-doc-tro     .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su catena movimenti                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
       ctl-rig-doc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale catena movimenti            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine lettura : uscita                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se buffer catena movimenti a spaces : riciclo   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-buf        =    spaces
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work di  *
      *              * lavoro                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo riga a spazi : riciclo                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig (1)    =    spaces
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-100.
       ctl-rig-doc-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo routine di controllo impostazioni su   *
      *              * riga corpo                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-imp-rig-000      thru ctl-imp-rig-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se zero errori riscontrati : riciclo su lettura *
      *              * catena                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-ele    =    zero
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione buffer errori                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to    w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr     .
       ctl-rig-doc-220.
           add       1                    to    w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine scansione : riciclo su lettura ca-  *
      *                  * tena                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr    >     w-ctl-imp-rig-ele
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda che si tratti o meno di un *
      *              * errore bloccante                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-bte
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)   =    "B"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-300
           else if   w-ctl-imp-rig-bte
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)   =    "N"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-400.
       ctl-rig-doc-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errore bloccante                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Composizione messaggio completo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing numero riga                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione stringa                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           string    "Errore a riga "
                                delimited by   size
                     v-edt      delimited by   spaces
                     " : "      delimited by   size
                     w-ctl-imp-rig-bmg
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-err-box-err-msg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione messaggio di errore               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di uscita ad errore                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-ctl-rig-doc-flg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A uscita                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-rig-doc-900.
       ctl-rig-doc-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errore non bloccante                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se flag di risposta operatore a X : riciclo *
      *                  * su scansione buffer errori                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-rig-doc-tro    =    "X"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-220.
       ctl-rig-doc-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Box di avviso con conferma impostazioni     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio immagine video              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Video in Off                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Box                                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      04                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      77                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Messaggio nel box                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Linea 01                            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Editing numero riga             *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rig-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Composizione stringa            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-alf                  .
           string    "Avviso per riga "
                                delimited by   size
                     v-edt      delimited by   spaces
                     " : "      delimited by   size
                     w-ctl-imp-rig-bmg
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)
                                delimited by   size
                                          into v-alf                  .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Visualizzazione stringa         *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      70                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Linea 02                            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      70                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Si confermano ugualmente le impostazioni (S/N) ? [
      -              " ]"                 to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Video in On                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Accettazione della risposta             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   v-alf                  .
       ctl-rig-doc-422.
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      56                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "EXIT"               to   v-pfk (20)             .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Set del tipo risposta da operatore      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su function-key impostata      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "N"            to   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-426
           else if   v-key                =    "DO  "
                     move  "X"            to   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-426
           else if   v-key                =    spaces
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-424
           else      go to ctl-rig-doc-422.
       ctl-rig-doc-424.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test su valore impostato se Return  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        v-alf                =    "N"
                     move  "N"            to   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-426
           else if   v-alf                =    "S"
                     move  "S"            to   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-426
           else      go to ctl-rig-doc-422.
       ctl-rig-doc-426.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino immagine video               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       ctl-rig-doc-440.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo di risposta *
      *                  * da operatore                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-rig-doc-tro    =    "N"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-442
           else if   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro    =    "S"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-444
           else if   w-ctl-rig-doc-tro    =    "X"
                     go to ctl-rig-doc-446.
       ctl-rig-doc-442.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo di risposta : No                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di uscita ad errore                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-ctl-rig-doc-flg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A uscita                                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-rig-doc-900.
       ctl-rig-doc-444.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo di risposta : Si                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su scansione buffer errori      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-rig-doc-220.
       ctl-rig-doc-446.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo di risposta : Si, e con omissione di   *
      *                  * altri messaggi                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo su scansione buffer errori      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-rig-doc-220.
       ctl-rig-doc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino area w-rig                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sav-wrk-rig        to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino area catena                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sav-cat-rig        to   w-cat-rig              .
       ctl-rig-doc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo su impostazione tasto Do riga corpo             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rig-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tdo-rig-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-rig-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo routine di controllo impostazioni su   *
      *              * riga corpo                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-imp-rig-000      thru ctl-imp-rig-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda del numero di errori ri-   *
      *              * scontrati                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-ele    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-120
           else      go to cnt-tdo-rig-140.
       cnt-tdo-rig-120.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se zero errori riscontrati                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A normalizzazioni                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-rig-200.
       cnt-tdo-rig-140.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riscontrati errori                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione buffer                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to    w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr     .
       cnt-tdo-rig-142.
           add       1                    to    w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr     .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se fine scansione e non sono stati tro- *
      *                      * vati errori Bloccanti : a normalizza-   *
      *                      * zioni                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr    >     w-ctl-imp-rig-ele
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Emissione messaggio                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-ctl-imp-rig-bmg
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)   to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Deviazione a seconda del tipo errore    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-ctl-imp-rig-bte
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)   =    "B"
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-144
           else if   w-ctl-imp-rig-bte
                    (w-ctl-imp-rig-ctr)   =    "N"
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-146.
       cnt-tdo-rig-144.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se tipo errore : Bloccante              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * A uscita con errore                 *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-rig-900.
       cnt-tdo-rig-146.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se tipo errore : Non bloccante          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo su scansione buffer         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-rig-142.
       cnt-tdo-rig-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo di esposizione della riga di fattura   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-epz-rgf (1)    =    zero
                     move  1              to   w-rig-epz-rgf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione flag di estensione alla de-  *
      *                  * scrizione prodotto                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-des-ext-000      thru det-des-ext-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Attivazione flag di accettazione valuta per *
      *                  * fatturazione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-tes-fda-vpf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento comodi di visualizzazione     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AG"                 to   w-edt-qta-inc-ope      .
           move      w-rig-qta-ven (1)    to   w-edt-qta-inc-qta      .
           move      w-rig-dec-qta (1)    to   w-edt-qta-inc-dec      .
           perform   edt-qta-inc-000      thru edt-qta-inc-999        .
           move      w-edt-qta-inc-din    to   w-tes-dec-qta          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuale attivazione segnale di riga       *
      *                  * successiva da pre-cablare                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Normalizzazione preliminare flag        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-pcr-rec-flg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su personalizzazione               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-snx-rae        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se riga nuova                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se addebito presente               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-add-pro (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Attivazione del flag                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-pcr-rec-flg      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Salvataggio valori per il pre-cablaggio *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-add-pro (1)    to   w-sav-rig-prc-add      .
           move      w-rig-qta-ven (1)    to   w-sav-rig-prc-qta      .
           move      w-rig-num-pro (1)    to   w-sav-rig-prc-pro      .
       cnt-tdo-rig-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuale messaggio di prodotto con addebi- *
      *                  * to al seguito                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su personalizzazione               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-snx-rae        not  = "S"
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se riga di addebito                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se riga nuova                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se addebito presente               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-add-pro (1)    =    zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se quantita' modificata            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-qta-ven (1)    =    w-sav-qta-ven
                     go to cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Messaggio di avviso                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "Verificare la quantita' della riga successiva !"
                                          to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
       cnt-tdo-rig-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita con esito positivo                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-rig-999.
       cnt-tdo-rig-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento errore                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di uscita ad errore                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-rig-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-rig-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo impostazioni su riga corpo                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       ctl-imp-rig-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inizializzazione numero elementi nel buffer er- *
      *              * rori                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-ctl-imp-rig-ele      .
       ctl-imp-rig-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su codice prodotto                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "C" or
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-020.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore non a zero : oltre                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-num-pro (1)    not  = zero
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-020.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione messaggio                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "Manca il codice prodotto                       "
                                          to   w-ctl-imp-rig-msg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo errore : Bloccante                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "B"                  to   w-ctl-imp-rig-ter      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione errore                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-imp-rig-900      thru ctl-imp-rig-909        .
       ctl-imp-rig-020.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su descrizione in riga                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore a spazi ammesso solo per tipi riga   *
      *                  * 'C'                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-des-rig (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-040.
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "C"
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-040.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione messaggio                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "Manca la descrizione                           "
                                          to   w-ctl-imp-rig-msg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo errore : Bloccante                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "B"                  to   w-ctl-imp-rig-ter      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione errore                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-imp-rig-900      thru ctl-imp-rig-909        .
       ctl-imp-rig-040.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su quantita' di vendita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "C" or
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-060.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se valore a zero                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-qta-ven (1)    not  = zero
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-060.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione messaggio                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "Manca la quantita'                             "
                                          to   w-ctl-imp-rig-msg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fattura accompagnatoria, tipo errore     *
      *                  * bloccante, altrimenti, tipo errore non      *
      *                  * bloccante                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    03
                     move  "B"            to   w-ctl-imp-rig-ter
           else      move  "N"            to   w-ctl-imp-rig-ter      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione errore                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ctl-imp-rig-900      thru ctl-imp-rig-909        .
       ctl-imp-rig-060.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su sigla valuta per il prezzo              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-int-ftr        =    01
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-070.
           if        w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "C" or
                     w-rig-tip-rig-tpr (1)
                                          =    "A"
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-070.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se valore a spaces                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-sgl-vpp (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to ctl-imp-rig-070.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione messaggio                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "Manca la sigla valuta per il prezzo            "
                                          to   w-ctl-imp-rig-msg      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo errore : Bloccante                     *
