      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda che il tipo movimento  *
      *                  * interessi la fatturazione                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     att-nmz-doc-110
                     att-nmz-doc-120
                     att-nmz-doc-130
                     depending            on   w-tes-int-ftr          .
           go to     att-nmz-doc-200.
       att-nmz-doc-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo movimento : non interessa la fattura-  *
      *                  * zione                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Attribuzione numero bolla               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-num-doc        to   w-att-bci-ndo-num      .
           move      w-tes-dat-doc        to   w-att-bci-ndo-dat      .
           move      w-tes-cod-dpz        to   w-att-bci-ndo-dpz      .
           move      w-tes-tip-mpb-sgl    to   w-att-bci-ndo-sgl      .
           move      w-tes-tip-mpb-nmm    to   w-att-bci-ndo-nmm      .
           perform   att-bci-ndo-000      thru att-bci-ndo-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se errore : uscita                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-att-bci-ndo-flg    not  = spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-att-nmz-doc-flg
                     go to att-nmz-doc-999.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero attribuito in destinazione       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-att-bci-ndo-num    to   w-tes-num-doc          .
           go to     att-nmz-doc-200.
