      *                      * Italia                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-doc        to   w-att-fti-prt-dat      .
           perform   att-fti-prt-000      thru att-fti-prt-999        .
           move      w-att-fti-prt-num    to   w-tes-fti-prt (1)      .
           go to     att-nmz-doc-200.
       att-nmz-doc-200.
