           if        w-tes-cod-dpz       not  = 1
                     go to ctl-slc-doc-828.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Oltre                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     ctl-slc-doc-830.
       ctl-slc-doc-825.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
