      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Primo vettore                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-pie-vet-aac (1)    to   w-pie-cod-vet (1)      .
           move      w-pie-vet-aac-des (1)
                                          to   w-pie-cod-vet-des (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Secondo vettore                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-pie-vt2-aac (1)    to   w-pie-cod-vt2 (1)      .
           move      w-pie-vt2-aac-des (1)
                                          to   w-pie-cod-vt2-des (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
