           move      w-pie-vt3-aac (1)    to   w-pie-cod-vt3 (1)      .
           move      w-pie-vt3-aac-des (1)
                                          to   w-pie-cod-vt3-des (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-vlp-vet-999.
