           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      70                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ripristino immagine video                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       ctl-tot-scc-900.
