      *    * e trattamento scadenze                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Eventuali assestamenti                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-pie-ass-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su segnale di si/no scadenze modificabile  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-snx-ims (1)    not  = "S"
                     go to exe-exp-pie-ass-900.
       exe-exp-pie-ass-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Azzeramento accumulatore spese incasso          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-tot-sic-wpa      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo 1..96                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-exp-pie-ctr      .
       exe-exp-pie-ass-200.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-exp-pie-ctr      .
      *
           if        w-exe-exp-pie-ctr    >    w-pie-scd-ele (1)
                     go to exe-exp-pie-ass-900.
      *
           if        w-exe-exp-pie-ctr    >    96
                     go to exe-exp-pie-ass-900.
      *
           if        w-pie-scd-tip
                    (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)
                                          =    zero
                     go to exe-exp-pie-ass-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione indice di comodo per tipo paga-  *
      *              * mento                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-pie-scd-tip
                    (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)
                                          to   w-exe-exp-pie-inx      .
           if        w-exe-exp-pie-inx    >    w-exe-exp-pie-max
                     move  01             to   w-exe-exp-pie-inx      .
           if        w-exe-exp-pie-inx    =    zero
                     move  01             to   w-exe-exp-pie-inx      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento causale contabile                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-prs-gep-cau-cge
                    (w-exe-exp-pie-inx)   to   w-pie-scd-cau
                                              (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione eventuali spese incasso associa- *
      *              * te alle scadenze                                *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * ATTUALMENTE INIBITO - DA PERFEZIONARE           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
______*    perform   exe-exp-pie-sic-000  thru exe-exp-pie-sic-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-ass-200.
       exe-exp-pie-ass-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Memorizzazione totale spese incasso calcolate   *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * ATTUALMENTE INIBITO - DA PERFEZIONARE           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-ass-999.
      *
           move      w-det-tot-sic-wpa    to   w-pie-tot-sic (1)      .
           if        w-det-tot-sic-wpa    =    zero
                     go to exe-exp-pie-ass-999.
       exe-exp-pie-ass-920.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento castelletto iva                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-agg-cst-iva-tip      .
           move      w-tes-civ-spi (1)    to   w-agg-cst-iva-coi      .
           move      w-pie-tot-sic (1)    to   w-agg-cst-iva-imp      .
           perform   agg-cst-iva-000      thru agg-cst-iva-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento castelletto contropartite         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-agg-cst-ctp-tip      .
           move      w-tes-ccp-spi (1)    to   w-agg-cst-ctp-cod      .
           move      w-pie-tot-sic (1)    to   w-agg-cst-ctp-imp      .
           perform   agg-cst-ctp-000      thru agg-cst-ctp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-ass-999.
       exe-exp-pie-ass-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Espansione dati piede per visualizzare il castelletto Iva *
      *    * e trattamento scadenze                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Determinazione spese incasso calcolate per scadenze       *
      *    * manuali                                                   *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * ATTUALMENTE INIBITO - DA PERFEZIONARE                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-pie-sic-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se codice spesa incasso non esistente : uscita  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-add-spi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se valuta del documento non e' quella di base : *
      *              * uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    not  = c-sgl
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
       exe-exp-pie-sic-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su signola scadenza                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su tipo pagamento                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-scd-tip
                    (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)
                                          =    zero
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura record [zin]                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODSPI    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-tes-add-spi (1)    to   rf-zin-cod-spi         .
           move      w-pie-scd-tip
                    (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)
                                          to   rf-zin-tip-pag         .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzin"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zin                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito operazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
      
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo funziona-   *
      *                  * mento spesa incasso                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-zin-tfu-spi       =    01
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-220
           else if   rf-zin-tfu-spi       =    02
                     go to exe-exp-pie-sic-240.
       exe-exp-pie-sic-220.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo funzionamento : automatico                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento accumulatore importo spese    *
      *                  * incasso                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       rf-zin-amm-spi       to   w-det-tot-sic-wpa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
       exe-exp-pie-sic-240.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo funzionamento : manuale                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
       exe-exp-pie-sic-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-sic-999.
       exe-exp-pie-sic-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Espansione dati piede per visualizzare il castelletto Iva *
      *    * e trattamento scadenze                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Ripristino castelletto scadenze                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-pie-rip-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul tipo di uscita                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-acc-sng-scd-esc    =    spaces
                     go to exe-exp-pie-rip-050.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A ripristino                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-rip-100.
       exe-exp-pie-rip-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se in modifica dati provvigionali          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-pie-rip-060.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sulla forma di pagamento                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su segnale di si/no scadenze modifica- *
      *                  * bili                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-snx-ims (1)    =    "S"
                     go to exe-exp-pie-rip-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A ripristino                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-rip-100.
       exe-exp-pie-rip-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo 1..96                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sav-scd-ele        to   w-pie-scd-ele (1)      .
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-exp-pie-ctr      .
       exe-exp-pie-rip-200.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-exp-pie-ctr      .
      *
           if        w-exe-exp-pie-ctr    >    96
                     go to exe-exp-pie-rip-900.
      *
           move      w-sav-scd-tbl
                    (w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)   to   w-pie-scd-tbl
                                              (1, w-exe-exp-pie-ctr)  .
           go to     exe-exp-pie-rip-200.
       exe-exp-pie-rip-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-pie-rip-999.
       exe-exp-pie-rip-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
