      *                  * posita personalizzazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-snx-buf-doc    =    "N"
                     go to buf-doc-mvm-405.
           if        rf-bit-ide-ute       not  = w-buf-doc-mvm-ute
                     go to buf-doc-mvm-200.
       buf-doc-mvm-405.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
